            <td class="nowrap" valign="top"><strong>onClose</strong></td>

            <td class="nowrap" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>

            <td valign="top">
                <p>Event fired when *after* the dialog box is closed.&nbsp;</p>

                <p>For executing functions *before* the closing of the dialog
                box, see the &#8220;buttons&#8221; attribute.</p>

                <p>The callback function (if any) receives as argument the
                caption of the clicked button or boolean FALSE if the dialog
                box is closed by pressing the ESC key or by clicking on the
                overlay.</p>
